-- Mediobanca's Investors Allow Bollore to Buy as Many as 8.9 Million Shares
-- B y   D a n   L i e f g r e e n   a n d   S o n i a   S i r l e t t i
-- 2010-09-21T14:45:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/mediobanca-s-investors-allow-bollore-to-buy-as-many-as-8-9-million-shares.html
Mediobanca SpA’s controlling
shareholders said investor Vincent Bollore can purchase as many
as 8.9 million shares that must be placed within the group’s
custody. Mediobanca gave the information in a stock-exchange
statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Liefgreen at 
 dliefgreen@bloomberg.net  